  <Docs>
    <summary>Provides options for encoding an XPS document with <see cref="SkiaSharp.SKDocument.CreateXps(SkiaSharp.SKWStream,SkiaSharp.SKDocumentXpsOptions)" />.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKDocumentXpsOptions` controls how an XPS document is generated. Set `Dpi` to specify the document resolution and `AllowNoPngs` to control whether pages without PNG images are permitted.

## Examples

```csharp
var options = new SKDocumentXpsOptions { Dpi = 300f, AllowNoPngs = true };
using var stream = File.OpenWrite("output.xps");
using var doc = SKDocument.CreateXps(stream, options);
using var canvas = doc.BeginPage(595f, 842f);
// draw content...
doc.EndPage();
doc.Close();
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
